## My Configuration Files ##

Probably not useful to you if you're not trying to be me

    git clone git@github.com:PerilousApricot/dotfiles.git
    mv dotfiles/.git ~/.config-git
    rm -rf dotfiles
    alias cgit="GIT_DIR=$HOME/.config-git GIT_WORK_TREE=$HOME/. git"
    cgit checkout .gitignore
    cgit status

Will update the files and show you what you're missing

